<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10017932>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Species of Rheumatobates from state of Rio Grande do Norte. (A–C) Rheumatobates crassifemur schroederi, (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views of apterous male, (C) dorsal view of macropterous male (distal part of forewing removed). (D–F) Rheumatobates minutus flavidus, (D) dorsal and (E) ventral views of apterous male, (F) dorsal view of macropterous female. (G–I) Rheumatobates trinitatis, (G) dorsal and (H) ventral views of apterous male, (I) dorsal view of apterous female. Scale bars = 1.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10017932/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

